    "+ heatmap"

  },

   ],
   "source": [
    "bw = \"../../../tests/test_data/bigwig_chr9_4000000_6000000.bw\"\n",
    "\n",
    "frame = XAxis() + \\\n",
    "    BigWig(bw) + \\\n",
    "    BigWig(bw) + Color(\"#fcbe07\") + HistStyle(\"line\", ) + \\\n",
    "    BigWig(bw) + Color(\"red\") + HistStyle(\"line\", fmt='o') + \\\n",
    "    BigWig(bw) + HistStyle(\"line\") + Feature(color=\"#000000\", threshold='250') + \\\n",
    "    BigWig(bw) + Color(\"#fcbe07\") + HistStyle(\"scatter\") + \\\n",
    "    BigWig(bw) + Color(\"#fcbe07\") + HistStyle(\"heatmap\")\n",
    "\n",
    "frame.plot(\"chr9:4700000-4950000\")"
